Indian) and Nordic (Alaska Native) Indigenous communities and mentioned the Navajo and other American Indian communities from the USA as well. We found no publications from Eurasia.&#8221;</p><p>A correction has been made to <xref rid="T1" ref-type="table">Table 4</xref>. The corrected table appears below.</p><table-wrap position="float" id="T1" orientation="portrait"><label>Table 4</label><caption><p>Dog bite risk factors identified by the studies included in the scoping review (some studies may have been classified in more than one categories).</p></caption><table frame="hsides" rules="groups"><thead><tr><th rowspan="1" colspan="1"/><th valign="top" align="center" colspan="3" style="border-bottom: thin solid #000000;" rowspan="1">
